content:
Yaagangall kaikkollllunnon- ammayumaayu chengaalikalle
Aachaaryanu samarppichu- thaathan chernnathu kaikkondu.
Mrthyupure nyaan chennetthi- mrtharodudghoshicheedum
Mariyaamil rakshakanudayam- cheythu nijeshdaal naranaayi
Prathyaashaavahasandesham- chonnevam vrddhan shemaon
Than praarththhana nammallkkennum- balamereedum praakaaram.?
